name: DadJokeoftheDay
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dad's funny daily joke
Developer Terms of Use
des: Each day, Alexa will choose from a list of hundreds of dad jokes; then, she will choose one to tell you for the day. Simply say "Alexa, run Dad's Funny Daily Joke" and she will tell you the first line of her joke. To hear the second line, just say something like "what is it?" or "what?" and she will deliver the punch line.
priv:
Developer Privacy Policy
The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
